OL,7,FThe ITV documentary, titled Her
OL,8,FMajesty The Queen: Behind Closed
OL,9,FDoors, captures a year of the Queen's
OL,10,Fprivate engagements focused on
OL,11,Fdomestic abuse, including her meetings
OL,12,Fwith survivors and visits to refuge
OL,13,Fcentres.
OL,15,FSpeaking to Good Morning Britain about
OL,16,Fthe upcoming documentary, Sharon said:
OL,17,F"There's not a lot of awareness around
OL,18,Fwhat coercive control looks like.
