OL,3,CPolice chief reveals how domestic
OL,4,Cabuse left her 'totally isolated' in
OL,5,Cnew film
OL,7,F"I was punished for being home late
OL,8,Ffrom work, I was told I was ugly, and
OL,9,Fslowly your friends are told they are
OL,10,Fno good for you, and then your family.
OL,11,FThen one day you look around and you
OL,12,Frealise that you are all alone and
OL,13,Fthey have isolated you.
OL,15,F"I kept silent for a long time and I
OL,16,Fwanted to speak out because silence is
OL,17,Fpower for the abusers. I was really
OL,18,Fworried about speaking out because no
OL,19,Fone looked like me or sounded like me."
