OL,7,FShe said: "There are invisible chains
OL,8,Fthat are created, especially when you
OL,9,Fhave children. You're not just
OL,10,Fthinking about yourself, you're
OL,11,Fthinking about people, little human
OL,12,Fbeings, that you're responsible for."
OL,14,FAnother described the moment her
OL,15,Festranged husband tried to kill her.
