OL,7,FShe said: "I can see him reaching into
OL,8,Fa bag and I can see him pulling this
OL,9,Fsawn off shotgun out of the bag. He
OL,10,Fhit me with the butt of the gun...he
OL,11,Fpointed the gun at my chest, told me
OL,12,Fhe loved me and pulled the trigger."
OL,14,FStatistics highlighted in the
OL,15,Fdocumentary underscore the prevalence
OL,16,Fof domestic abuse, with one in five
OL,17,Fadults affected and three women dying
OL,18,Fby suicide each week due to abuse.
