OL,7,FA domestic abuse-related call is made
OL,8,Fto emergency services every 30
OL,9,Fseconds, yet only 24% are estimated to
OL,10,Fbe formally reported.
OL,12,FThe Queen said: "One of the most
OL,13,Fdifficult things about domestic abuse,
OL,14,Fto understand, it's not the bruises
OL,15,Fand the black eyes, which,
OL,16,Funfortunately you see, through
OL,17,Fviolence, this is something that
OL,18,Fcreeps up very slowly and, far too
OL,19,Foften, it ends up with women being
OL,20,Fkilled.
