OL,7,F"You meet somebody, you think they're
OL,8,Fwonderful and attractive and love
OL,9,Fyou...and then bit by bit, they start
OL,10,Fto undermine you. They take away your
OL,11,Ffriends, they take away your
OL,12,Ffamily...and then when you start
OL,13,Fquestioning it...these people become
OL,14,Fvery violent."
